---
const funnel = [
  { view: '_Job', desc: 'The anchor — one row per send', color: '#6b7280' },
  { view: '_Sent', desc: 'The denominator — who we sent to', color: '#0055ff' },
  { view: '_Open', desc: 'Engagement — who opened', color: '#0d9488' },
  { view: '_Click', desc: 'Engagement — who tapped a link', color: '#0d9488' },
  { view: '_Bounce', desc: 'Delivery failures', color: '#d97706' },
  { view: '_Unsubscribe', desc: 'Opt-out events', color: '#dc2626' },
];
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Send Analysis — SFMC Data Views</title>
    <style>
        :root { --accent: #0055ff; --ink: #1a1a1a; --muted: #666; --line: #e1e4e6; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 20px 64px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.6; }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 0 28px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        .back-link:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
        h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.6rem); margin: 16px 0 8px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
        .lede { font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.15rem); color: var(--muted); margin: 0 0 40px; max-width: 60ch; }
        .funnel-intro { font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--muted); margin: 0 0 20px; }
        .funnel { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
        .stage { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 20px; background: #fff; }
        .stage-view { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; min-width: 120px; }
        .stage-desc { color: var(--ink); font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .arrow { text-align: center; color: #ccc; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1; }
        .principles { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
        .principle { border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; }
        .principle h3 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 1rem; }
        .principle p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); }
        code { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace; background: #f6f8fa; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 4px; padding: 2px 6px; font-size: 0.85em; }
        .cta { display: inline-block; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
        .cta:hover { background: #0044cc; }
        @media (max-width: 560px) {
            .stage { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 4px; }
            .stage-view { min-width: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to projects</a>
    
    <h1>Email Send Analysis with SFMC Data Views</h1>
    <p class="lede">
        Connecting Salesforce Marketing Cloud's system data views into a single send-to-engagement funnel —
        so one email send can be traced from delivery through opens, clicks, bounces, and opt-outs.
    </p>

    <p class="funnel-intro">The funnel — every view traces back to the Job</p>
    <div class="funnel">
        {funnel.map((stage, i) => (
            <div>
                <div class="stage" style={`border-left: 4px solid ${stage.color}`}>
                    <span class="stage-view" style={`color: ${stage.color}`}>{stage.view}</span>
                    <span class="stage-desc">{stage.desc}</span>
                </div>
                {i < funnel.length - 1 && <div class="arrow">↓</div>}
            </div>
        ))}
    </div>

    <div class="principles">
        <div class="principle">
            <h3>One anchor key</h3>
            <p>Every event view joins back to <code>_Job</code> on <code>JobID</code>, with <code>JobID + SubscriberKey</code> identifying a subscriber within a send.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle">
            <h3>Right key, right question</h3>
            <p><code>JobID</code> is one send; <code>EmailID</code> is the content across every send of it — choosing correctly is the whole game.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle">
            <h3>Delivered = not bounced</h3>
            <p>SFMC has no positive delivery view, so delivery is derived as <code>_Sent</code> minus <code>_Bounce</code> — simple and reliable.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/projects/sfmc-email-analytics" class="cta">Read the full technical breakdown →</a>
</body>
</html>